                <div class="tcard"><div class="tcard-stars"><i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i><i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i><i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i><i class="bi bi-star-fill"></i><i class="bi bi-star-half"></i></div><p class="tcard-text">"Triple Kabab Burger is massive and so filling. Great value for money. The shami kabab is also amazing. Will keep ordering!"</p><div class="tcard-author"><div class="tcard-avatar">MF</div><div><div class="tcard-name">Muhammad Farhan</div><div class="tcard-loc">Clifton, Karachi</div></div></div></div>
